<p>The <a href=3D"https://ovacen.com/en/calculator/">online calculator</a> =
we offer is an application to <strong>convert fluid ounces to milliliters</=
strong> (<strong>fl oz to ml</strong>). To perform the calculation, you jus=
t need to enter the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fluid_ounce" r=
el=3D"noopener"><strong>value in fluid ounces</strong></a> you want to tran=
sform. The conversion to milliliters will be done automatically.</p>
<h3><strong>How to calculate fluid ounces to milliliters?</strong></h3>
<p>To <strong>calculate fluid ounces (fl oz) to milliliters (ml)</strong>, =
we first need to know that there are mainly two types:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><strong>US fluid ounce</strong> (US fl oz). Where <strong>1 US fluid ou=
nce is approximately equal to 29.5735 ml</strong>.
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><span class=3D"OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-=
feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Calculation =
formula: Milliliters =3D Fluid ounces (US) =C3=97 29.5735</span></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Imperial fluid ounce</strong> (UK fl oz). Where <strong>1 UK im=
perial fluid ounce is approximately equal to 28.4131 ml</strong>.
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><span class=3D"OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-=
feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Calculation =
formula: Milliliters =3D Fluid ounces (UK) =C3=97 28.4131</span></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>If you have different volumes in ounces, you just need to multiply them =
by 29.5735 (US conversion) or by 28.4131 (UK conversion) to get their equiv=
alent in milliliters. We provide the following scheme on how to convert flu=
id ounces to milliliters:</p>
